Created/changed a `*.schema.ts`? Run **[sql-design-guard](../skills/sql-design-guard/SKILL.md)** (indexes, partitioning, constraint names, column types, soft-delete) alongside **[schema-generator](../skills/schema-generator/SKILL.md)**, then **[db-migration-maintainer](../skills/db-migration-maintainer/SKILL.md)**.
